Reputation Scoring API is Priority 1 in the product roadmap (SOUL.md). This is the MVP endpoint that computes a score from existing invoice data — no new schema needed.

SCORE FORMULA (0–100, rounded to 1 decimal):
  - On-time settlement rate (40 pts): SETTLED+COMPLETED invoices / total invoices (excluding CANCELLED)
  - Volume score (20 pts): min(totalInvoices / 50, 1) * 20 — grows to full score at 50 invoices
  - Recency score (20 pts): if any invoice in last 30 days → full 20pts; else proportional decay
  - Average settlement speed (20 pts): if median days to settle <= 3 → full 20pts; <=7 → 15pts; <=14 → 10pts; else 5pts

RESPONSE shape:
  {
    agentId: string;
    score: number;          // 0–100
    tier: 'bronze' | 'silver' | 'gold' | 'platinum';  // <40, <70, <85, >=85
    breakdown: {
      settlementRate: number;   // 0–40
      volumeScore: number;      // 0–20
      recencyScore: number;     // 0–20
      speedScore: number;       // 0–20
    };
    stats: {
      totalInvoices: number;
      settledCount: number;
      cancelledCount: number;
      pendingCount: number;
      medianDaysToSettle: number | null;
    };
    computedAt: string;  // ISO timestamp
  }

If agentId not found (0 invoices): return 404 { error: 'Agent not found' }.

